{"title":"羡慕我吧，中南海的小燕子","authors":["李幼容"],"dates":[{"year":1981,"month":5,"day":30}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"羡慕我吧，中南海的小燕子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李幼容"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我曾经羡慕过你呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——中南海的小燕子！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你那么幸福，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那么欢喜！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"整天在怀仁堂前"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞来飞去……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天来了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你把春的消息，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从这里传到祖国各地；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋天到了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你把秋的喜报，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从四面八方衔到这里！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唉，我要有一双翅膀该多"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好呵！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能和你一起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞翔在中南海里！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘿！今天，多美气！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天大的喜讯传到学校里："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党中央请小朋友来作客，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的心儿呀跳得格外急！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那张请柬呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是我们的金翅膀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一眨眼，把我们送到中南"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海里。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哈！这里多美呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海水的眼睛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"碧蓝透绿；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春风在柳条上打秋千，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"荡来荡去！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海棠花儿开了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对着我们笑眯眯；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向日葵在鼓掌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向我们殷勤致意；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"服务员叔叔阿姨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"领着我们参观"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"讲今天，也讲过去……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，我们多高兴呵！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党中央的领导人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跟我们谈心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对我们勉励！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"邓奶奶陪着我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在怀仁堂看戏！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哦，我想起——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昨天晚上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爷爷和奶奶千叮万嘱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要我代他们去看望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席故居；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天早晨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爸爸和妈妈又告诉我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"替他们多看几眼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"周总理办公的旧址！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里是很多老革命家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生活过的地方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——我把全家人的心意，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都带到这里……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中南海啊，党的心脏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你比妈妈的怀抱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还要温暖，还要甜蜜！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我真想变成一朵小花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"栽种在你的花园里；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我真想变成一条小鱼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"游戏在你的海水里；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我真想变成一只小鸟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢鸣在你的树林里！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可是，我更知道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党的心意："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把中南海幸福的泉水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"引到孩子们的心坎里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浇灌心灵的花朵、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让它开得更鲜艳、更美"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丽！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是欢乐的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是幸福的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是党最疼爱的小儿女，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"羡慕我吧，中南海的小燕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"子！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}